data.description: Welcome to this delightful piece of history nestled in the heart of the desirable Crestwood neighborhood in Fort Worth. This classic 1942 home exudes character and boasts an incredibly structure, ready for your personal touch and modern updates. This spacious 2,235 sq ft home offers ample room for a growing family or anyone seeking generous living space. With 4 bedrooms, everyone can have their own private space or even create a home office! With character, history, and a fantastic structure to renovate and make your own, this 1942 Crestwood home is a must-see. Don't miss this unique opportunity to be part of the Crestwood community and create the home of your dreams!
